"type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-wisdom-al-hikmah","tag-animals","tag-drink-al-sharab","tag-food-al-taam","tag-health","tag-medicine-al-tibb","tag-milk-al-laban","tag-sickness-al-marad","tag-trees"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-6HN","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":37915,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/06\/23\/rivers-in-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":25779,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Jannah: Rivers of water, milk, honey, and wine in Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 23, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019awiyah ibn Haydah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, in Paradise there is a sea of water, a sea of honey, a sea of milk, and a sea of wine, and thereafter they branch into rivers.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2571 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35309,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/27\/parable-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":25779,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dunya: Worldly life is like good food becoming excrement","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 27, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Dahhak ibn Sufyan reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said to him, \u201cO Dahhak, what are you eating?\u201d He said, \u201cMeat and milk.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThen what will it become?\u201d He said, \u201cYou know what it will become.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32616,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/03\/rinse-mouth-drink-milk\/","url_meta":{"origin":25779,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Milk: Rinsing the mouth after drinking milk","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, drank some milk and rinsed his mouth. The Prophet said, \u201cIt contains fatty grease.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 208, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 358 Grade:\u00a0Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim Al-Tirmidhi said, \u201cSome of the scholars held\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26776,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/08\/27\/dua-barakah-food-drink\/","url_meta":{"origin":25779,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication for blessings after eating, drinking","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 27, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever is provided food from Allah, let him say: O Allah, bless us in it and feed us with what is even better. Whoever is provided a drink of milk from Allah, let him say: O\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4541,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/09\/fasting-shield-battle\/","url_meta":{"origin":25779,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Siyam: Fasting is like a shield in battle","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 9, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Uthman ibn Abi al-'As reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFasting is a shield from the Hellfire, just like a shield of yours in battle.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 1639 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u062b\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0635\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13720,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/24\/barakah-enjoy-blessings-moderation\/","url_meta":{"origin":25779,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Blessings: Enjoy blessings of Allah in moderation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 24, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cEat, drink, and give in charity. Wear nice clothing, but without pride or extravagance. Verily, Allah loves for His blessings to be seen upon His servants.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 6708 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/25779","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=25779"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/25779\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=25779"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=25779"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=25779"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}